Package: PlantHealth
Title: Plant Health Monitoring Based on Vegetation Indices from Sentinel-2 satellite image
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Abran", "Idrees", , "abranidrees333@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides farmers, agronomists, and stakeholders with an accessible and fast interface for assessing crop health monitoring, making intelligent decisions, and reducing fertilizer consumption. This facilitates precision farming, cost savings, and sustainable agricultural practices by offering trustworthy vegetation indices and data visualization tools. Its open-source nature facilitates cooperation and provides flexibility to changing demands, resulting in increased production and global food security.
